Section1.Para:
The meteorological and the AQ models participating in AQMEII are: 


WRF – CMAQ;



WRF/MM5 – CAMx;



MM5 – CHIMERE;



COSMO – MUSCAT;



MM5 – DEHM;



MM5 –POLYPHEMUS;



LOTOS – EUROS;



ECMWF – SILAM;



GEM – AURAMS;



PARLAM-SP – EMEP;



WRF – WRF/Chem.

                Some AQ models were run over the two continents driven by different meteorology (as for example, CAMx). Full details, settings and references can be found in Solazzo et al. [2]. In total there are eleven AQ models that were run over EU and seven AQ models over NA. The models’ outputs were compared against observational data at over 1,000 receptor locations over the two continents.
